cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with path planning and interference management for a network of cellular-connected UAVs, which involves topics related to networked systems (cs.NI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep reinforcement learning and echo state networks further supports the inclusion of cs.AI and cs.LG as likely sub-categories.
